<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#netAmount> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#netAmount> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Final redistribution amount for this member (grossAmount - costDeduction)." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#netAmount> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#netAmount> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "net amount" .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Committed flexibility amount in kWh. Positive value; direction is expressed by hasFlexibilityDirection." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#targetFlexibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "target flexibility" .
# 
# 
# 
# #################################################################
# #
# #    Classes
# #
# #################################################################
# 
# 
# http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#ConceptScheme
<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#ConceptScheme> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
# 
# https://purl.org/peco/peco-core#EnergyCommunity
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommunityContext
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommunityContext> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommunityContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Operational context binding a PECO Energy Community\n    with assets, datasets, simulations and flexibility commitments." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommunityContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommunityContext> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Community Context" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommunityContext> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:ctx1 a celine:CommunityContext ;\n    celine:hasCommunity    ex:rec_valdarno ;\n    celine:usesAsset       ex:pv_panel_01 ;\n    celine:hasSimulation   ex:sim_baseline ;\n    celine:hasCommitment   ex:fc_001 ;\n    celine:hasSettlementRun ex:sr_2025_q3 ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostItem
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostItem> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A named cost voice within a SettlementRun (e.g., administrative fee,\n    platform fee, outstanding debt). Enables transparent cost breakdown before redistribution\n    amounts are finalised." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostItem> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Cost Item" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostItem> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:cost_admin a celine:CostItem ;\n    celine:hasCostType  celine:AdminCost ;\n    dct:description     \"Community administration fee Q3 2025\" ;\n    celine:costAmount   \"120.00\"^^xsd:decimal .\n\nex:cost_platform_fee a celine:CostItem ;\n    celine:hasCostType  celine:Fee ;\n    dct:description     \"CELINE platform usage fee Q3 2025\" ;\n    celine:costAmount   \"45.00\"^^xsd:decimal ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#DatasetReference
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#DatasetReference> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#DatasetReference> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Reference to an external dataset used as input or produced as output.\n    CELINE does not define dataset schemas." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#DatasetReference> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#DatasetReference> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dataset Reference" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#DatasetReference> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:ds_irradiance a celine:DatasetReference ;\n    dct:identifier  \"irradiance-2025-07\" ;\n    dct:source      <https://data.example.org/weather/irradiance> ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A member's pledge to provide a specific amount of flexibility\n    on one or more of their PODs during a given time window. The commitment can be\n    automated (device-driven) or voluntary (manually activated by the member)." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Flexibility Commitment" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCommitment> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:fc_001 a celine:FlexibilityCommitment ;\n    celine:committedBy              ex:member_rossi ;\n    celine:onPOD                    ex:pod_rossi_heatpump ;\n    celine:hasCommitmentMode        celine:Automated ;\n    celine:hasFlexibilityDirection  celine:FlexDown ;\n    celine:targetFlexibility        \"2.5\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:hasTimeInterval          ex:interval_2025_07_01 ;\n    celine:generatesCredit          ex:cr_001 ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityConstraint
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Operational constraint governing when and how flexibility declared in a\n    FlexibilityEnvelope may be activated. Encodes timing rules (minimum notice period, minimum\n    and maximum activation duration, recovery time between activations) and frequency limits." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Flexibility Constraint" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityConstraint> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:constraint_hp a celine:FlexibilityConstraint ;\n    celine:hasConstraintType     celine:DurationConstraint ;\n    celine:minNotificationTime   \"PT15M\"^^xsd:duration ;\n    celine:minActivationDuration \"PT30M\"^^xsd:duration ;\n    celine:maxActivationDuration \"PT4H\"^^xsd:duration ;\n    celine:minRecoveryTime       \"PT1H\"^^xsd:duration ;\n    celine:maxActivationsPerDay  \"3\"^^xsd:integer ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCredit
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCredit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCredit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Credit awarded to a member for fulfilling (fully or partially)\n    a FlexibilityCommitment. Denominated in kWh and backed by metered SOSA observations.\n    Credits accumulate until reconciled in a SettlementRun." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCredit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCredit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Flexibility Credit" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityCredit> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:cr_001 a celine:FlexibilityCredit ;\n    celine:earnedBy     ex:member_rossi ;\n    celine:creditFor    ex:fc_001 ;\n    celine:creditAmount \"2.1\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:evidencedBy  ex:obs_pod_rossi_20250701T10 ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Declared capability of a Point of Delivery (POD) to provide flexibility\n    within a given availability window. Captures the physical bounds — maximum upward and downward\n    power and available energy — that constrain any FlexibilityCommitment drawn from it.\n    Aligned with saref4ener:PowerProfile for device-level scheduling semantics." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Flexibility Envelope" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <https://saref.etsi.org/saref4ener/> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#FlexibilityEnvelope> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:env_hp a celine:FlexibilityEnvelope ;\n    celine:envelopeFor           ex:pod_rossi_heatpump ;\n    celine:maxFlexUp             \"2.0\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:maxFlexDown           \"3.0\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:availableEnergy       \"6.0\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:hasAvailabilityWindow ex:window_morning ;\n    celine:hasConstraint         ex:constraint_hp ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A definition of a KPI type, independent of any specific evaluation.\n    Captures the name, description, formula, unit, scope, calculation method and temporal\n    granularity of a KPI. Instances may simultaneously be skos:Concept members of the\n    celine:KPICatalog controlled vocabulary."@en .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Definizione KPI"@it .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "KPI Definition"@en .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#closeMatch> <https://saref.etsi.org/saref4city/KeyPerformanceIndicator> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:kpi_def_ssr a celine:KPIDefinition , skos:Concept ;\n    skos:inScheme           celine:KPICatalog ;\n    celine:hasKPIName       \"Self-Sufficiency Rate\" ;\n    celine:hasKPIDescription \"Ratio of locally consumed energy to total consumption.\"@en ;\n    celine:hasKPIScopeType           celine:ScopeCommunity ;\n    celine:hasKPICalculationMethod   celine:MethodRatio ;\n    celine:hasKPITemporalGranularity celine:GranularityPeriod ;\n    celine:hasKPIUnit                celine:Dimensionless ." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#relatedMatch> <http://bigg-project.eu/bigg4kpi#BuildingKeyPerformanceIndicator> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Evaluation of a KPI for a specific scope entity and time interval.\n    References a KPIDefinition for the metric type, and carries the computed value,\n    the evaluation period, and optional provenance links to observations or upstream\n    KPI evaluations."@en .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "KPI Evaluation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Valutazione KPI"@it .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#closeMatch> <http://bigg-project.eu/bigg4kpi#KPIAssessment> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#closeMatch> <https://saref.etsi.org/saref4city/KeyPerformanceIndicatorAssessment> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#KPIEvaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:kpi_eval_ssr_q3 a celine:KPIEvaluation ;\n    celine:hasKPIDefinition        celine:SelfSufficiencyRate ;\n    celine:hasKPIValue             \"0.72\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:hasEvaluationTimeInterval ex:interval_q3_2025 ;\n    celine:hasEvaluatedScope       ex:ctx1 ;\n    celine:hasInputObservation     ex:obs_meter_001 ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#RedistributionResult
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#RedistributionResult> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#RedistributionResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The calculated redistribution outcome for a single member within a\n    SettlementRun. Records credit balance (kWh), gross monetary value before deductions,\n    the member's allocated share of community costs, and the final net amount." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#RedistributionResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#RedistributionResult> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Redistribution Result" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#RedistributionResult> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:result_rossi a celine:RedistributionResult ;\n    celine:resultFor        ex:member_rossi ;\n    celine:creditBalance    \"2.1\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:grossAmount      \"0.252\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:costDeduction    \"0.048\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:netAmount        \"0.204\"^^xsd:decimal ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Scenario
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Scenario> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Scenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Definition of assumptions, temporal scope and configuration\n    for one or more simulations." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Scenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Scenario> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Scenario" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Scenario> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:sc_summer a celine:Scenario ;\n    rdfs:label              \"Summer 2025 baseline\" ;\n    dct:description         \"24-hour simulation with historical irradiance data.\" ;\n    celine:hasTimeInterval  ex:interval_2025_summer ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SettlementRun
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SettlementRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SettlementRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Execution of the redistribution calculation for a settlement period.\n    Aggregates FlexibilityCredits across all members, applies a linear conversion rate\n    (kWh -> monetary), deducts shared cost voices (CostItems), and produces one\n    RedistributionResult per member." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SettlementRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SettlementRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Settlement Run" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SettlementRun> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:sr_2025_q3 a celine:SettlementRun ;\n    celine:settlesContext           ex:ctx1 ;\n    celine:hasTimeInterval          ex:interval_q3_2025 ;\n    celine:conversionRate           \"0.12\"^^xsd:decimal ;\n    celine:currency                 \"EUR\" ;\n    celine:hasCostItem              ex:cost_admin, ex:cost_platform_fee ;\n    celine:hasRedistributionResult  ex:result_rossi, ex:result_bianchi ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Simulation
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Simulation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Simulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Abstract simulation definition independent from execution." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Simulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Simulation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Simulation" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Simulation> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:sim1 a celine:Simulation ;\n    celine:hasScenario      ex:sc_summer ;\n    celine:hasSimulationRun ex:run_001 ." .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SimulationRun
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SimulationRun> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SimulationRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Concrete execution of a Simulation under a specific Scenario." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SimulationRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SimulationRun> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Simulation Run" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#SimulationRun> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "ex:run_001 a celine:SimulationRun ;\n    celine:usesDataset      ex:ds_irradiance ;\n    celine:producesDataset  ex:ds_energy_forecast ;\n    celine:hasKPIEvaluation ex:kpi_self_sufficiency ." .
# 
# 
# 
# #################################################################
# #
# #    Individuals
# #
# #################################################################
# 
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Overhead and management costs for operating the REC." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostType> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Administrative Cost" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#AdminCost> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CostType> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Commitment fulfilled automatically by a smart device or control system, without manual intervention from the member." .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommitmentMode> .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Automated" .
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#Automated> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommitmentMode> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommitmentMode
<https://w3id.org/celine-eu#CommitmentMode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
